summary: I’m loving the Spider-Man series so far but...they had the chance to make MJ a complete badass who could handle herself in...
body:
I’m loving the Spider-Man series so far but…they had the chance to make MJ a complete badass who could handle herself in battle and they didn’t. I know she is actually useful, she’s not a complete damsel in distress, but I would’ve loved to see her fighting some bad guys too, instead of Spidey telling her to hide while he takes care of it. It’d be so cool to see them fighting off some bad guys side by side.

Of course I know nothing about Spider-Man so maybe this is weird?

summary:
Baby Morgan is born
Peter is absolutely in love with his little sister
She’s the best
Every second he’s not on Spider Duty or at...
body:
Baby Morgan is born

Peter is absolutely in love with his little sister

She’s the best

Every second he’s not on Spider Duty or at school he’s hanging out with Morgan

Morgan’s second word was Peter and her fourth was spider (her first was daddy not that anyone was surprised)

Peter was Morgan’s favorite superhero

And whenever he came into the room, suited up or not, her eyes would light up and she would bounce up and down

But one day just after Morgan’s 3rd birthday

There was an accident

Morgan only knew 2 things

The first was that her daddy had been in the lab a lot after the accident and even when she did see him he never smiled anymore

Sometimes she heard yelling from the lab

Sometimes he muttered “I should’ve been there” but she didn’t know what that meant either

And two is that her favorite big brother had stopped visiting

One day at dinner she asked “where’s Peter?”

But her dad just dropped his fork and ran out of the room

And her mom just looked down

A couple days later there was a big party for him at their house

At least that’s what her mom called it

It didn’t feel like a party

Because he wasn’t there

And everyone was crying

~

It was Morgan’s 10th birthday when her dad handed her a present

“He told me to give this to you when you hit the big double digits” he said cracking a half smile

She smiled in return but apparently her dad could tell she was confused

“Peter. Your favorite older brother” he said trying to lighten the situation, but she could tell he was getting upset

“Who?”

His face dropped

She could see tears in his eyes but she didn’t remember saying anything wrong

He walked out of the room

She opened the present

It was a really old iron man mask toy with a note on the inside

“From one superfan to another

Love, Peter”

There was also a picture of Morgan as a baby

A teenage boy was holding her

She was laughing

She smiled down at the picture

And suddenly she remembered

She remembered Peter

And the accident

And the party

But it wasn’t a party

She went down to the lab and handed her dad the old picture

He took it into his hands, holding it like it was the rarest thing in the world. He smiled.

After a couple minutes Morgan finally broke the silence

“I wanna know what happened to Peter”
